data.title: Zorro's Black Whip - Linda Stirling, 1st Female Zorro, The Full 12 Chapter Serial – Titta på Film & TV-program
data.meta_description: Hammond, owner of the town's stagecoach line & a leading citizen, is secretly opposed to Idaho becoming a state, & conducts raids against citizens to prevent order. Barbara, played by Linda Sterling, an expert with a bullwhip & pistol, dons a black costume becoming Zorro's "Black Whip", (The 1st female Zorro character) dealing a blow to Hammond & his gang each time they perform some heinous act.
